		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Looks very interesting. What tools/assembler/SDK are you using for creating of the game? Are you going to release the sourcecode? Do you plan to use some kind of compression (For the graphic tiles it will work very good) or you will put the raw data in the ROM?
<br />
<br />16KB shall be enough, but if you compress everything, you will have much more free space for Title Screens, Intro, Tutorial, Manual and most importantly - Music.

		

